data.description: This "Hidden Gem" is situated on a "3 Lot Site" located in a quiet neighborhood. Home was built in 2006 with a Tile Roof and offers 3 bedroom/ 2.5 bath plus den with French doors which can easily be converted into a 4th bedroom and a covered front porch area. This lovely home is very spacious offering 2,015 sq.ft. of living area and a Oversized Undercover Lanai that includes a half bath which is perfect while entertaining family and friends and also ideal for future pool plans. The Owners Suite offers a large bedroom with private access to the lanai and a large walk-in closet. The second and third bedroom offers much privacy with a large guest bath. A separate access to the Oversized Lanai from the kitchen and family room with triple sliders. New Construction throughout this neighborhood, Why wait to build? When you can purchase this and put your own finishing touches without the Price Tag! Endless Opportunities for the Right Buyer. Call and schedule your private showing today.
